hidden_constraints.oracle_response:
When options.global=true and config.global_namespace is set, the output starts with 'export {}
declare global {
  export namespace <namespace_value> {

', then each declaration is indented by 4 spaces, and the file ends with '  }
}
'. The namespace value comes from config.global_namespace (e.g., 'App.Models').

